&lt;p&gt;Post: MSK Senior Specialist Physiotherapist Band 7&lt;br /&gt;Hours: 33.5&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you hard-working, innovative and have a passion for MSK Physiotherapy?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Within central Manchester we have a very experienced community physiotherapy team that includes a consultant physiotherapist, Advanced Physiotherapy Practitioners, Band 7 and Band 6 physiotherapists. We are looking for a highly specialised MSK Physiotherapist to join our team and manage one of the clinical hubs within our service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates must demonstrate good experience working within community musculoskeletal outpatients, have experience of clinical supervision of students and junior members of staff and have been involved with the management and development of an MSK service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;MFT are committed to supporting staff with continual professional development. Personal and professional training opportunities are available via internal courses and through strong links to local Universities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are keen to meet candidates who have the skills, drive and motivation to develop themselves, the service and ensure the provision of an effective and evidence based Physiotherapy to the people of Manchester.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact&lt;/p&gt;
